📍sizzle town
✧ ✧ ✧
comment some video suggestions/what you’d like to see from me! (bowl vids, clay mix, bubble pops...)
+ drop a⚡️if you spotted the glitch lol
✧ ✧ ✧
it’s already july 😥
i’m back from my brief hiatus with some fresh videos! sorry for the unannounced break, but i really just wanted to chillax and live in the moment after graduation so i didn’t need to worry about anything while out of town and starting my summer activities~ but i’ll definitely be more active now! still unsure about what i’ll do when i head off to college, but i’ll try to only post new videos and have a restock by then 😃👍 love y’all and thanks for sticking with me ❤️ ps: this video is from my freshman year of hs and now i’m an incoming college freshman 😳
✧ ✧ ✧
shop is stocked; link in bio!
save if you like this post ♡
shopify: slimepeony.com
etsy: slimepeony.etsy.com
next restock: tbd
